OPENROUTER_API_KEY=your_openrouter_api_key_here

# =============================================================================
# SETUP INSTRUCTIONS
# =============================================================================
#
# This is an EXAMPLE file. Do NOT rename it to .env for deployment.
# 
# Cloudflare Workers use environment variables configured in the dashboard,
# NOT local .env files (except for local development with wrangler dev).
#
# =============================================================================
# HOW TO GET YOUR OPENROUTER API KEY
# =============================================================================
#
# 1. Go to https://openrouter.ai/
# 2. Sign up or log in to your account
# 3. Navigate to "Keys" section in your dashboard
# 4. Create a new API key
# 5. Copy the key (it looks like: sk-or-v1-...)
#
# =============================================================================
# HOW TO ADD THE KEY TO CLOUDFLARE (REQUIRED FOR PRODUCTION)
# =============================================================================
#
# AFTER deploying your worker with `npx wrangler deploy`:
#
# 1. Go to https://dash.cloudflare.com/
# 2. Select your account
# 3. Click "Workers & Pages" in the left sidebar
# 4. Click on your worker name (e.g., "personal-news-digest")
# 5. Go to "Settings" tab
# 6. Scroll to "Environment Variables"
# 7. Click "Add variable"
# 8. Variable name: OPENROUTER_API_KEY
# 9. Value: paste your OpenRouter API key
# 10. Click "Encrypt" (recommended)
# 11. Click "Save"
#
# The worker will automatically restart with the new environment variable.
#
# =============================================================================
# LOCAL DEVELOPMENT (OPTIONAL)
# =============================================================================
#
# If you want to test locally with `npx wrangler dev`:
#
# 1. Copy this file: cp .env.example .dev.vars
# 2. Edit .dev.vars and replace "your_openrouter_api_key_here" with your real key
# 3. Run `npx wrangler dev`
#
# Note: .dev.vars is already in .gitignore and will NOT be committed.
#
# =============================================================================
# SECURITY NOTES
# =============================================================================
#
# - NEVER commit your real API key to git
# - NEVER share your .dev.vars file
# - Use encrypted environment variables in Cloudflare dashboard
# - Rotate your key immediately if it's exposed
# - Monitor your OpenRouter usage dashboard for unexpected activity
#
# =============================================================================